    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a refined balance of performance and long-term reliability. Featuring a documented service history and robust mechanical components, it represents a premier acquisition for the discerning driver. Its condition reflects consistent care and professional upkeep, ensuring immediate road-readiness and sustained value. We invite you to experience the superior engineering and aesthetic appeal of this exceptional automobile.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
